quran[96]{c,v,t}:
  56,1,Nihaboneka ikizoboneka
  56,2,Ukuboneka kwaco s’ikinyoma
  56,3,Kizo tetereza abantu babi n’uguha iteka abantu beza
  56,4,"Mugi he Isi izo nyiganzwa, ikazo nyiganzwa bimwe vy’inguvu"
  56,5,N’imisozi igihe izo vungagurwa
  56,6,Ibe nk’inkungugu zitumuka
  56,7,Namwe muzoba muri mumice itatu
  56,8,Abantu bagira ineza bazoba bameze gute? Abo bantu bagira ineza
  56,9,N’abantu bagira ishari bazoba bameze gute? Abo bantu bagira ishari
  56,10,"N’abazoba\tbari\timbere\ty’abandi\tmu\tbagira\tineza\tnibo\tbazoba\tbari imbere y’abandi"
  56,11,Abo nibo bazohabwa ikaze n’Imana yabo
  56,12,Mu mirima izoba irimwo imigisha myiza ntangere
  56,13,Ahantu haniniya muri aba ni mubantu bambere
  56,14,N’uruhande rutoyi ni mubantu banyuma
  56,15,Bazoba bari hejuru y’inyegamo z’iteka zisharijwe neza
  56,16,Bazoba bazegamiye ko kandi barabana
  56,17,Babe bakikujwe n’imiyabaga igifise n’amashusho y’ubuyabaga akiri meza abereye kandi ateye igomwe
  56,18,"N’ibikombe\thamwe\tn’amabirika\tn’ibirahuri\tvy’ubunywero\tbivuye\tmu nzuzi aboneka mwo inzira yayo mazi"
  56,19,"Ntibazo meneka imitwe yabo kubera ivyo binyobwa, canke ngo batakaze ubwenge bwabo"
  56,20,N’ivyamwa vy’ubwoko bwose nkuko bavyipfuza
  56,21,N’inyama z’inyoni nkuko bavyifuza bonyene
  56,22,N’abapfasoni bafise amaso meza kandi manini maniniya
  56,23,Nk’ubutare bwitiriwe Ilulu bunyegejwe
  56,24,N’impembo y’ivyo vyose bahora bagira
  56,25,Muriyo ntibazo kwumva amajambo ataco abamariye canke amajambo y’ibicumuro
  56,26,Atari amajambo y’amahoro n’ayandi gusa
  56,27,"N’aba\tbantu\tb’amahoro\tnabo\tbazoba\tbameze\tgute?\tabo\tbantu b’amahoro"
  56,28,Bazoba bari munsi y’ibitutu vy’ibiti bidafise amahwa
  56,29,N’ingundu z’ibitoki bitondeshejwe neza hamwe n’imivyaro yazo myiza
  56,30,No mu bitutu bigororotse kumpande zose
  56,31,N’amazi ashunguruka neza
  56,32,N’ivyamwa vyinshi vy’ubwoko bwose
  56,33,Ntakama ayo mazi kandi ntabuzwa
  56,34,N’ubusaswa bwabo buri hejuru
  56,35,Twebwe twabaremye mw’ishusho ryiza cane
  56,36,Tuzobagira amasugi nkuko aribwo bwambere bubaka izabo
  56,37,Bakundana n’abacance b’abo
  56,38,Kubera abantu bagira ineza
  56,39,Uruhande runiniya muribo nu rw’abantu baho hambere
  56,40,N’urundi ruhande runiniya nurw’abantu banyuma
  56,41,N’abantu b’ishari bazoba gute abo bantu b’ishari
  56,42,Bazoba bari mu muyaga w’umuriro n’amazi abira nk’amarike
  56,43,N’igitutu c’umwotsi wirabura cane
  56,44,Sicu kuzana akayaga gakanye canke icu kuruhukira mwo
  56,45,"Ntankeka\tbo\tbari\timbere\ty’ibi\tvyose\tbibereye\tmu\tbuzima bw’amahirwe"
  56,46,Bamye bafatiriye ku bicumuro bininiya
  56,47,"Bamye\tbavuga\tbati:-\tnitwapfa\ttukaba\tivu\tn’amagufa\tmasa\tniho tuzozurwa"
  56,48,Canke abavyeyi bacu bakera
  56,49,"Vuga uti:- ntankeka abambere n’abanyuma"
  56,50,Bazo kwegeranywa bose kumwanya wategekanijwe no k’umusi uzwi
  56,51,"Hanyuma\tmwebwe\tmwazimiye\tn’uguhakana\tImana\tyanyu\ty’ukuri"
  56,52,Mu vy’ukuri mwebwe muzofungura kugiti citiriwe Zaqqumum
  56,53,Kuri ico giti muzo kwuzuriza mwo inda zanyu
  56,54,No hejuru y’ayo muzonywa amazi ashushe y’amarike
  56,55,"Kandi\tmuzonywa\tnkakumwe\tkw’ingamiya\tziyanywa zifise\tinyota\tya cane"
  56,56,Iyo niyo nzimano yabo yuwo musi w’impembo
  56,57,Ni twebwe twabaremye mugabo ntimutwemera
  56,58,Mbega murabona intanga muteragira
  56,59,Mbega ni mwebwe muzi rema canke ni twebwe tuzirema
  56,60,"Twebwe twabateguriye urupfu, rero ntituzonanirwa n’ukubazura"
  56,61,"Ntituzonanirwa\tkuzana\tabandi\tbantu\tatari\tmwebwe\tn’ukuba\trema murindi shusho mutazi"
  56,62,"Ntankeka mwebwe murafise ubumenyi bw’iremwa ryambere, none ni kuki mutibuka"
  56,63,Mbega murabona ibiterwa mutera
  56,64,Mbega ni mwebwe mubinagisha canke ni twebwe tubinagisha
  56,65,"Iyo dushaka twari kubagira abadafise ubwenge, mukaguma mwidoga gusa"
  56,66,Mu vy’ukuri twebwe twarigoreye ubusa
  56,67,Ahubwo twebwe twarahakaniwe
  56,68,Mbega murabona amazi munywa
  56,69,Mbega ni mwebwe mwayamanuye muyakuye mubicu canke ni twebwe tuyamanura
  56,70,"Iyo\tdushaka\ttwari\tkuyagira\tay’umunyu\tukaze\tcane,\tnone\tni\tkuki mudashima"
  56,71,Mbega mwebwe murawubona umuriro mwatsa
  56,72,"Mbega\tigiti\tcawo\tni\tmwebwe\tmwakiremye\tcanke\tni\ttwebwe twakiremye"
  56,73,Twebwe twagize ico giti kuba nk’icibutso n’akamaro ku bantu bose
  56,74,Rero ninahaza izina ry’Umuremyi wawe mukuru
  56,75,Rero ndarahiye kw’iseruka ry’Inyenyeri
  56,76,Mu vy’ukuri iyo ntankeka n’indahiro niniya iyo mubi menya
  56,77,Ntankeka iki n’igitabu cegeranye ibikenewe vyose kandi gifise iteka n’icubahiro
  56,78,Icavuye muri ico gitabu kiziganijwe neza cane
  56,79,Nta muntu agikora ko atari mu bantu bisukuye n’amabi yose
  56,80,N’imanuka ry’aco ryavuye ku Muremyi w’ibiremwa vyose
  56,81,Mbega murakengera ibi biganiro
  56,82,Kandi mukagira imigisha yanyu muyi kengera namwe muyi hakana
  56,83,Mbega igihe umutima w’umuntu uzoba washitse mu muhogo
  56,84,Namwe muri ico gihe muraba
  56,85,Natwe twegeranye nawe cane gusumba mwebwe namwe mutabona
  56,86,"Nk’uko mwebwe mutari\tk’ubutegetsi bwanje"
  56,87,None ni kuki mutosubiza uwo mutima nimwaba mu vugisha ukuri
  56,88,Niyaba ari muri bamwe bahawe ikaze n’Imana
  56,89,N’akanyamuneza ntangere hamwe n’akamoto keza hamwe n’imirima irimwo imigisha myiza ibarorereye
  56,90,Niyaba ari mu bantu beza b’intungane
  56,91,"Rero izobabwirwa iti:- n’amahoro y’Imana kuri wewe, kuko uri mu bantu b’intungane"
  56,92,"Niyaba yari mu bantu b’abahakanyi b’Imana y’ukuri, kandi bazimiye"
  56,93,Inzimano yiwe n’amazi ashushe y’amarike
  56,94,N’uguhira mu muriro udahera
  56,95,Ntankeka uku niko kuri nyakuri
  56,96,Rero n’uninahaze izina ry’Umuremyi wawe nyene iteka rikuru